  "remarks": "\nIn both a personal capacity and as a leader of FPRC and CPC fighters, Mahamat SALLEH Adoum Kette has been responsible for serious violations of international humanitarian law in the Central African Republic in relation to rape and other forms of sexual and gender-based violence.  \n",
